{
  "chapter": 22,
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你一定要回来。",
      "tone": "恳切",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_die",
      "text": "一定！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我能不能进来？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "请进。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我看来怎么样？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "你还是老样子，好像永远都不会变的。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你没有看清楚，其实我已经老了很多。",
      "tone": "嫣然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "这一年来，我的日子并不大好过——也许每个人的日子都不会很好过，所以每个人都会老的。",
      "tone": "轻叹",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你什么话都不必说了，我明白！",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "你……你不怪我？",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "每个人都有权为自己打算，若换了我，我也会这样做的！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "她对你好不好？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "那么你日子就一定过得很好，我早就知道，只有一个真正对你好的女人，才能令你这样的男人幸福。",
      "tone": "羡慕",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我不明白的是，你既然过得很好，为什么要回来呢？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "你真的想不到？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你若是回来替老伯拜寿，只怕已迟了一步。",
      "tone": "叹气",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "迟了一步？……难道老伯出了什么事？",
      "tone": "动容",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "谁也不知道他出了什么事，谁也不敢到他那花园去，但每个人都知道他一定出了事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "因为这地方忽然变得很乱，好像每天都有很多陌生人来来去去……",
      "tone": "描述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "也许只有你可以去看看他，你们的关系毕竟和别人不同。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你用不着顾虑我，我只不过想来看看你，随时都可以走的。",
      "tone": "体贴",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "你……是不是要回家？",
      "tone": "迟疑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "除了回家外，我还有什么地方好去？",
      "tone": "幽幽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "家里是不是还是老样子？",
      "tone": "关切",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "怎么会还是老样子！",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "幸好还有石群在。",
      "tone": "宽慰",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "石群也不在。",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "自从我去年叫他到西北去之后，他就一直没有回来，也没有消息。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "他怎么会出事？据我所知，西北那边没有人能制得住他的。",
      "tone": "骇然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "谁知道呢？江湖中的事，每天都可能有变化，何况一年呢？",
      "tone": "叹气",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "老朋友都一个个地走了，我一个人有时也会觉得很寂寞，所以……所以你有空的时候，不妨回来看看我。",
      "tone": "黯然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "假如你能带着她回来，我更欢迎。",
      "tone": "展颜而笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我一定会回来看你……只要我不死，我一定会带她回去！",
      "tone": "握拳",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "马太太",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "text": "小中已经快十岁了，连一本三字经都还没有念完，你究竟想让他玩到什么时候？",
      "tone": "埋怨",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马方中",
      "listener": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "text": "也许我现在已经可以开始教他读书了。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "马太太",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "text": "其实你早就该开始了，我真不懂，你为什么要等到现在？",
      "tone": "松口气",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马方中",
      "listener": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "text": "有些事你还是不懂的好。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "马太太",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "text": "还有些什么事？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马方中",
      "listener": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "text": "男人的事，女人最好连问都不要问，时候到了，就自然会让你知道。",
      "tone": "正色",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "马太太",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "text": "什么时候，究竟是什么事？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马方中",
      "listener": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "text": "照现在这情况看来，那时候永远都不会到了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马方中",
      "listener": "char_ma_tai_tai",
      "text": "茶不错，喝了这杯茶，你先去睡吧！",
      "tone": "特别",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马方中",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "老伯呢？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "巨人",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "text": "你就是马方中？",
      "tone": "生涩",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马方中",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "我不是马方中，是方中驹。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    }
  ]
}